<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 4 (Yuri) - Start</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ヴェイグ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Veigue</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>フレン</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Flynn</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ユーリ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yuri</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>農作物が育たなくなっていたオレの故郷は
ある人の援助によって
なんとか生き長らえてきた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Due to the aid of a certain person,
we managed to survive in my hometown,
where crops could no longer be grown.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>みんなが生きていけるだけの
資材を送ってくれたその人は村の出身で
今は別の村の役人を務めていた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That person, who dispatched the raw material
that was enough for us to survive, came from
our village. He was now employed as a
government official in another village.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まさかそれは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You can't mean...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>オレ達の村の恩人を
お前が殺したんだ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You killed our village's benefactor...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>…………！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あの人はずっとオレ達を支えてくれた。
それだけじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That person always sustained us.
And that's not all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>オレの……オレのせいで
氷に包まれてしまった村のみんなを
救い出す方法も、考えてくれると言った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Because of me... Because of me and my
ice power, he said he would think of a way
to free everyone in the village.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんな人を、お前は……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And that person, you...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>オレはお前を許さない。
許す事は出来ない……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I will not forgive you.
I CAN'T forgive you for this...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>12</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
